# Project Rules & Agent Guidelines

## Project Overview

This is **Joshua's Recipe Collection** вЂ” a personal, static recipe web application built with Astro and Tailwind CSS v4. It is deployed as a GitHub Pages user site at `https://joshuasimon.github.io`. The project is in its first prototype (v1) and focuses on public recipe browsing with no authentication or backend.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Astro (v5+) вЂ” static site generation
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4 via `@tailwindcss/vite` Vite plugin (no `tailwind.config.js` вЂ” configured in CSS)
- **Content**: Astro Content Collections with Markdown (`.md`) files and Zod schema validation
- **Language**: TypeScript in strictest mode (`astro/tsconfigs/strict`)
- **Deployment**: GitHub Pages (user site вЂ” no base path)
- **Package Manager**: npm

